1. Initialize agent with username and password which creates wallet (Alice) 
2. Initialize a second agent using the same method above^
3. Send credential offer (message family is state?)`Sending "\{"type": "did:sov:BzCbsNYhMrjHiqZDTUASHg;spec/sovrin.org/ui/1.0/state", "content": {"initialized": true, "agent_name": "Bob"}}"`
4. Receive? `{{Received "\{"type":"did:sov:BzCbsNYhMrjHiqZDTUASHg;spec/sovrin.org/ui/1.0/state_request","id":"1ea43de7ae0f405b95fa3dca53843d6e","content":null}"}}

